duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide strategic consultancy and mentorship to leadership and Jira/Jira Align/Agile tools users.
Proactively seek out, collaborate, and establish relationships with critical business, technology, and enterprise partners.
Lead change, drive acceptance, and cultivate support across the organization.
Analyze and propose solutions to sophisticated problems using data analysis and agile tools.
Adapt quickly to a changing landscape while keeping focus on the outcome.
Engage as a trusted partner and proven change agent in the organization.
